{"tid":44013,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求評 7日岡山--宮島--博多之旅","createTime":"2016-12-18T02:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T08:12:58.000Z","uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd65e8a5dd871db1bb054e98324674197f63d5c","tid":44013,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"我諗住買 HK AIRLINE 來回岡山 20170320-0327 再買山陰山場7DAY JR PASS 去以下地方，我skip咗廣島，諗緊尾道個晚有冇咩平酒店甚至網吧都得，同埋博多2日有咩玩?<br />\n<br />\n0320晚<br />\n下午機到岡山-行一陣商場<br />\n宿--岡山<br />\n<br />\n0321<br />\n倉敷美觀<br />\n宿--岡山<br />\n<br />\n0322朝<br />\n岡山後樂園<br />\n之後JR往尾道<br />\n<br />\n0322晚<br />\n宿--尾道<br />\n<br />\n0323<br />\n尾道一天遊<br />\n往宮島宿<br />\n<br />\n0324<br />\n宮島一天遊<br />\n博多宿<br />\n<br />\n0325-0326<br />\n博多玩2日<br />\n<br />\n0327<br />\n由博多番岡山搭下午機番香港"},{"pid":"e5cbe7450c944ebf2e862ca2fa58135e89117b5e","tid":44013,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手睇睇"},{"pid":"7615206eb730c757dbd8093d09543f20f5681460","tid":44013,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6f271f0074f88ad6fa4bbe1d8bb6b361ad7b0732","tid":44013,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"21.22夾埋一齊都仲有時候剩"},{"pid":"817f28ac9cc3c90584943c5699aa1a58d5da8086","tid":44013,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>21.22夾埋一齊都仲有時候剩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呢個都只係係預鬆啲<br />\n可能22朝一早過到尾道放低行李就可以玩足一日<br />\n<br />\n仲諗緊如果可以可能尾道玩完直落宮島咁應該可以 多一日時間"},{"pid":"9005805767fa11cb0d792632a816c04aa023d4dd","tid":44013,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"下年6月去岡山留名"},{"pid":"7a9c99d2258edcaa3540425bc6b4069378dd6914","tid":44013,"uid":47128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"我買左HK airline 去岡山<br /